{"tid":2381911,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"連林志玲也輸了！「最美華人女星」排行出爐　冠軍竟是她","createTime":"2021-01-27T02:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T16:41:57.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":575,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"18eee700a8fc859eaa75944b41306948a371d2df","tid":2381911,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:35:00.000Z","msg":"為了吸引粉絲目光，各地區偶像、明星們都會講究穿著、妝容，迎合當地觀眾們的審美觀。日本網站《みんなのランキング》近期便讓日本人票選心中最喜愛的中港台女星，排行榜不久後曝光，受歡迎的大咖女神包含林志玲、范冰冰等人雖然都在榜上，卻並未拿下冠軍寶座，第一名反倒是「她」，讓鐵粉狂喊「實至名歸！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/08/02/2052697-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F08%2F02%2F2052697-PH.jpg&h=85b877d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「台灣第一名模」林志玲在排行中雖然只拿下第6名，不過仍獲得大批網友愛戴。（圖／翻攝自林志玲IG）<br />\n<br />\n該網站近期公開「最美華人女明星」排行榜，台灣知名女星林志玲、陳喬恩、林依晨、徐若瑄、王心凌、楊丞琳皆在榜上， 「台灣第一名模」林志玲更奪下第六名，不少投票的粉絲大讚「女神不僅有才華又聰明」、「微笑總是如此親切」、「臉蛋看起來依舊像25歲，叫她姐姐真的不為過」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/26/3001544-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F26%2F3001544-PH.jpg&h=a4ee6b0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼章子怡（上）、范冰冰（下）分別拿下第2、3名，人氣同樣居高不下。（圖／翻攝自章子怡、范冰冰微博）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/10/21/2197635-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F10%2F21%2F2197635-PH.jpg&h=13754c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一名寶座則由Angelababy（楊穎）抱走，網友紛紛在底下寫出投票動機，「她的臉蛋根本是完美等級，眼睛有如洋娃娃般，看見她的笑顏就瞬間被打動了」、「她的確是位稱職的演員和模特兒」、「五官精緻對稱、臉蛋找不出一絲破綻，若來生有機會再當女人，希望能擁有這樣的面孔」。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，Angelababy在2004年以模特兒身分出道後就掀起轟動，擁有德中混血的她，身材、外型均羨煞一票女性，甚至被日本名醫評選為「亞洲最佳整容範本」；另外，她也不時出現在螢光幕前展示亮麗穿搭、演藝新作，人氣可謂火速增長，更是微博熱搜的常客。<br />\n<br />\n榜單顯示，排行榜第1至10名分別為，Angelababy、章子怡、范冰冰、楊冪、陳慧琳、林志玲、龍夢柔、陳喬恩、迪麗熱巴、林依晨。徐若瑄、王心凌、楊丞琳則分別是12、16、17名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/11/06/2227406-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F11%2F06%2F2227406-PH.jpg&h=fdb1c621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼Angelababy拿下「最美華人女星」排行冠軍，姣好臉蛋、火辣身材羨煞不少女粉絲。（圖／翻攝自Angelababy微博）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/11/21/2894313-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F11%2F21%2F2894313-PH.jpg&h=c7310adb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/03/28/2477557-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F03%2F28%2F2477557-PH.jpg&h=895bcd14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c525caf7c0bc2b9f2728670615deda800982539f","tid":2381911,"uid":211461,"like":115,"dislike":8,"score":107,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:36:50.000Z","msg":"梁朝偉煙.gif<br />\n蝙蝠俠車.gif"},{"pid":"771a70b34110e4829a647de71d16ea74c1a70c53","tid":2381911,"uid":261849,"like":143,"dislike":3,"score":140,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:38:26.000Z","msg":"屌那星 整容閪第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88518499954a584f8c38103d82dd67873825e9ec","tid":2381911,"uid":5725,"like":102,"dislike":4,"score":98,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:39:56.000Z","msg":"召喚你的樣子如何"},{"pid":"9731e7cacb854dc3b377f5a806b1d22c95d94cab","tid":2381911,"uid":232229,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:40:15.000Z","msg":"陳慧琳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d2e16aa23e626641f55be5108b26653e0a5e93","tid":2381911,"uid":56912,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:40:39.000Z","msg":"陳慧琳有分都幾驚訝"},{"pid":"b54d796a2f888f22d165db4bff9a399c3adf2c44","tid":2381911,"uid":16659,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"quote":{"pid":"c525caf7c0bc2b9f2728670615deda800982539f","tid":2381911,"uid":211461,"like":115,"dislike":8,"score":107,"c